#: app/main.cpp:486
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Latte is a dock based on plasma frameworks that provides an elegant and "
"intuitive experience for your tasks and plasmoids. It animates its contents "
"by using parabolic zoom effect and tries to be there only when it is "
"needed.\n"
"\n"
"\"Art in Coffee\""
msgstr ""
"Latte je dok postavený na Plasma frameworkoch, ktorý poskytuje elegantný a "
"intuitývny zážitok pre vaše úlohy a plasmoidy. Oživuje svoj obsah pomocou "
"parabolického efektu priblíženia a pokúša sa byť tam iba keď je to "
"potrebné.\n"
"\n"
"\"Umenie v Káve\""

